reviewText: Samantha B is always adorable! Bought this for our friends and they also love it!

My family came from Holland many years ago. I always wanted to visit. This DvD changed my mind. Amsterdam is a city that is to heavy into drugs. I was totally surprised. I am retired law enforcement and don't want to see that sort of thing.
Sorry.
The Dvd came on time and the price was good and arrived in good condition,
It would not load in blue-ray player, only on the computer! It is just plain JUNK!
